11 April 2018 Park- and ride facility for Winnie Madikizela-Mandela memorial Government reminds mourners who are attending the memorial services for struggle stalwart Winnie Madikizela-Mandela this morning to make use of the park-and-ride facilities from the Nasrec Expo Centre.The park-and-ride facilities are accessible at Nasrec Expo Centre 1 and Nasrec Expo Centre 2.Â  Buses are available only at these two pick up points to seamlessly move people to the Orlando stadium. The park-and-ride to the stadium this morning is operational until 9am. Roads around the stadium are closed to private vehicles. Enquiries:Ms Phumla WilliamsCell: 083 501 0139 Issued by Government Communication and Information System